2004-11-23 16:45 UTC+0100 Maurilio Longo <maurilio.longo@libero.it>
  * source/rtl/tbrowse.prg
    ! Fixed several incompatibilities in cell writing/highlighting
      To see what I mean, use tests/testbrw.prg _before_ this fix.
      In particular there were errors reguarding size of printed
      value, width of highlight cursor, default width in case
      no :width property is set in tbcolumn object.
      Removed DispCellNormal(), no need to duplicate all that code
      to save a couple of IFs, and inlined ColorToDisp() to make it
      a little faster, maybe.
      I've tested my fix with DBU, a case test on news.xharbour.org
      and my employer biggest app and, with all of them, it works ok.

